到设计师、高级工程师等各不相同。其中有人获得不错的收益，也有人扩大了人脉，更有人从零工兼职者转变为全职员工。但零工领域也存在不少问题，比如是否合规、合同的签订等。从「雇佣关系」转为「商业合作」 超 2 亿人进入零工经济 _ 用工 _ 就业 _ 企业"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-2d8e682ef3e9929d02b361357b3cee75_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "168 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/620467702"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI4+HulNebvJVaEAMaCTEwMDE2MTQ0NCDcqdWnBjAAOO4BQARyCTYyMDQ2NzcwMngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1693857775.551389", "card_id": "Q_620484106", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 39}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "缅甸「诈骗基地」妙瓦底一警察局遭到无人机多次投掷炸弹袭击，死亡人数已升至 5 人，哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据央视新闻 9 月 4 日最新消息，据当地媒体报道，当地时间 9 月 3 日，缅甸克伦邦妙瓦底的一警察局遭到无人机多次投掷炸弹袭击，导致 3 人当场死亡，十余人受伤。在医院救治过程中再有 2 人不治身亡。 截至目前，此次袭击造成的死亡人数已升至 5 人，其中包括多名当地地方官员和警务人员。缅甸「诈骗基地」妙瓦底被炸弹袭击！死亡人数已升至 5 人！臭名昭著的「KK 园区」就在这…"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "138 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/620484106"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I4+HulNebvJVaEAMaCTEwMDE2NTA5NyCE89WnBjAAOFdABXIJNjIwNDg0MTA2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1693857775.551949", "card_id": "Q_619814502", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 30}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "华为 Mate 60 Pro 可以卫星通话，是不是意味着不管有网没网，都可以随意拨打电话？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "108 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""},